True
False
True
True


and
op1     op2      result
True    True      True
True    False     False
False    True     False
False    False     False

print(True and False)  #False

if first operand is true  second operand must checking.
if first operand  is false  second operand not checking
any nonzero value    True 

3 and 5    5
0 and  5   0
3 and 0    0
0 and 0    0

